The paper discusses the impact of cognition on the energy efficiency of a downlink cellular system with multiple relays, which involves information theory (cs.IT), networking and communication (cs.NI), and system and control theory (cs.SY). The paper also mentions practical examples and numerical simulations, which could fall under multimedia (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories.
